headline: Prologis to Participate in Industry Conferences
summary: Prologis, Inc. (NYSE: PLD) today announced that Hamid Moghadam, co-founder, chairman and CEO; Dan Letter, president; and Tim Arndt, chief financial officer, will participate in the Citi 2025 Global Property CEO Conference at The Diplomat Beach Resort in Hollywood, Florida.
